    <h1>Data Deletion Instructions</h1>
    
    <p>We respect your privacy and provide multiple ways to delete your data from our system:</p>

    <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
            <h3>Option 1: Delete Through Facebook</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Go to your Facebook Settings & Privacy</li>
                <li>Click on "Settings"</li>
                <li>Go to "Apps and Websites"</li>
                <li>Find our app in the list</li>
                <li>Click "Remove" to revoke access and request data deletion</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h3>Option 2: Contact Us Directly</h3>
            <p>Send an email to [Your Support Email] with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Subject: "Data Deletion Request"</li>
                <li>Your Facebook-associated email</li>
                <li>Date you used our app</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We will process your request within 30 days and send a confirmation email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p>If you have any questions about data deletion, please contact our support team at [Your Support Email].</p>
